node.text:
✧･ﾟ: *✧･ﾟ:*fresh start!!*:･ﾟ✧*:･ﾟ✧⁣⁣
💕hey pals!! im back from my break! im so sorry for being gone, i was extremely busy with life and i needed to focus on sorting things out and finishing my finals, now that that’s done, here’s an idea of my new posting schedule i came up with! i will try my best to roughly stick to this 💗⁣
🌸i’ll start uploading on youtube this monday! i’ll upload shorts which may be my tiktoks, and i’ll be creating new long-form youtube content :) so excited for it! other than shorts, the first real youtube video i make will be my room tour!! make sure to sub to my youtube :)⁣
🌸i will also be posting often on my anime figure account! it’s @tiredarling so go follow it! ⁣
🌸twitch streams will be happening so soon!!! i’ll update y’all on the times but they may change weekly, but the days i hope to stream are there :) make sure to follow my twitch and maybe even sub!!⁣
🌸movie nights will happen on my discord every saturday and hope to be there each time! we will usually be watching anime 💕 i’ll have the discord link up soon! ⁣
🌸i’ll be going live on tiktok every sunday to chat with you guys and answer questions c:⁣
🌸linktree hooked me up with a cool premium account so my new improved bio link will be up soon!! itll have the links to all my socials and discord server 💕💕💕 thank you guys so much for waiting for me to come back from break, i cant wait to make even more content for you all🌱🌸💖 -junna/jo
